{"tid":883663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警偷耳機罰$2000　求情稱腰傷轉文職自覺無用","createTime":"2018-10-31T04:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T03:38:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"45d3e0fefc25c871798302265ea814136432c7e8","tid":883663,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181031/photo/bkn-20181031105743591-1031_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181031114313\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181031%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181031105743591-1031_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181031114313&h=82cae26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將屆退休年齡的54歲男警員，去年底休班期間在深水埗一間店舖內，涉嫌盜竊一對價值29港元的耳機，店員發現後報警將他拘捕。涉案被告張志良被控一項盜竊罪，今(31日)在西九龍法院承認控罪，被判罰款2000港元。案情指，被告在店內購物時從貨架上拿了兩條充電線及一個耳機，之後將耳機放入褲袋，僅拿充電線去付款。有店員目擊其犯案過程將他截住。 <br />\n<br />\n律師求情時指，被告1987年加入警隊，本來駐守水警，但一次他執勤時墮坡腰部受傷，要轉到警署報案室擔任文職。自始他感到自己「無用」，人生失意，出現焦慮、抑鬱，甚至有自殺傾向。 <br />\n<br />\n惟之後他的母親及胞妹更先後被診斷出患腦瘤及乳癌，他因而情緒低落，求助於警隊心理服務，才知悉自己的問題，他曾於聯合醫院精神科留醫達兩個月。律師強調被告一直奉公守法，就自己的行為感到非常後悔，他於上月已經退休。 <br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示案中失物價值不高，被告坦白承認控罪亦顯示悔意，遂判他罰款2000港元了事。裁判官更特意勸告被告，指他仍然年輕，日後仍能活出精彩人生，縱然過去他與家人均經歷不如意，希望他能積極努力走出低谷。被告聞言悲從中來，仍嗚咽着回應說明白。他亦得到10多名親友到庭支持。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181031/bkn-20181031105743591-1031_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181031%2Fbkn-20181031105743591-1031_00822_001.html&d=8px2%2Fe9R3OJ8fqB58kdGNBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5e5b13a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181031/bkn-20181031105743591-1031_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b1cc19f2346d95e9f520427546482dccc9e4b60","tid":883663,"uid":60287,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:22:15.000Z","msg":"d判詞唔講仲以為黑警先係受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5479c92cb1581cb0bc3a6134c0070e2a299f7d","tid":883663,"uid":54337,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"29蚊都偷，無用就梗㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察<br />\n正宗垃圾"},{"pid":"3a0bdd34000dbeb9d4d89957fd9c2648344306c2","tid":883663,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"訴諸憐憫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317c140b9ab1be874abb160b7f4692f95a2dee3e","tid":883663,"uid":199299,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:24:37.000Z","msg":"偷$29嘢 罰返$2000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> proud of hk police dogs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659b59e5be642dc093fb9f13bfb56cf9489ca4c8","tid":883663,"uid":60279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:24:41.000Z","msg":"原來依家偷野係計價計, 唔係計偷野依個動作<br />\n<br />\n姐係平野就任偷, 貴野就坐番十年8年"},{"pid":"c800d068c7f09a4b1fccf09ad94304dfd5851235","tid":883663,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91bd166e15b865cc1374111010569d91c7d881a5","tid":883663,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"好慘，五十五歲無得撈為非作歹"},{"pid":"daba17806f6fc7e0b3967648b6304a4681a3413d","tid":883663,"uid":199412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"咁樣仲有冇長俸？"},{"pid":"2e9fda7b4a1cd0fb18db9ceaacd147288b5d5cf0","tid":883663,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daba17806f6fc7e0b3967648b6304a4681a3413d","tid":883663,"uid":199412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:25:07.000Z","msg":"咁樣仲有冇長俸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"豬Sir都好似仲咬緊長糧，佢呢d偷少少野WFC <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222f65ecae84b